task.summary:
Lab 2
Added functionality for loading locally saved data if a user is logged in and displaying info on preferences profile layout.

Lab 2
Added functionality for locally saving settings. No actual effect on phone yet.

Lab 2
Made availability check before saving. onSaveClick checks availability, if character name is available, doSave is called, otherwise tell user to enter a new one.
Requested permissions from user, handled permissions accordingly.
Fixed bug with password popup when clicking outside of box.
Removed Sign In button click intent. Only way to access an account is to create it.
Added Toasts in various places to keep user informed on ongoing processes.

implemented sign-in functionality including saving data to local shared preferences. Developed splash screen with banner image and play button functionality. Test text not displaying. Will solve later.

Fixed test text for splash screen play button from earlier. Implemented last part of splash screen saying how many cats. This involved sending a GET request to get the list of cats and saving the length to shared preferences. Will probably want to save the whole array to shared preferences later.
Got Google Maps to show up in its own activity upon clicking play. Had to acquire an API key from Google.
Put markers for cat locations on the map. Tracked to current location. Not sure if current location works because we didn't have our physical phones with us.

Tested finding current location with physical phone. Was having problem because location was being returned as null. Debugged and found that we in fact did need the line saying requestLocationUpdates. In order to make that work, we needed to implement LocationListener.

LAB 3 COMMIT #7
Added banner to game activity, including displaying selected marker information: cat picture, cat name, distance to cat.
Added variables to keep track of selected cat for state preservation in life cycle.
Changed marker icons for cats. Changes color when selected.
Stored cat information (JSON Objects) in marker tags.
Deselects all markers when click on map.
Implemented pet button to send pet requests to the server.
Built success activity, including buttons to go back to game and back to menu.

LAB 3 FINAL COMMIT (#8)
Prevented zoom and scroll in Google Maps. Camera follows user's location
Implemented distance limit for markers.
Implemented real-time distance updates on selected cat.
Saved settings locally and on server, keeping data syncronized.
Created EditProfile actvitiy to edit profile information such as password and full name
Started SuccessActivity on successful pet.
Implemented a reset list button for debugging purposes.
Lateness on account of extension/24hr pass.

APK ADD
Attempting to add apk to gitlab. Unsure if working.

Lab #4 Commit #1
Developed the history tab.
Added the dependencies and gradle code in order to run the Camera Overlay code

Lab #4 Commit #2
Added camera overlay functionality
